EMPLOYMENT AGREEMENT

This Employment Agreement ("Agreement") is made effective as of {{start_date}} between:

Employer: {{company_name}} ("Company")
Employee: {{employee_name}} ("Employee")
Position: {{job_title}}
Department: {{department}}

1. EMPLOYMENT TERMS
The Company hereby employs the Employee in the position of {{job_title}}. The Employee agrees to devote full business time and best efforts to the Company.

2. COMPENSATION
Base Salary: {{annual_salary}} per year, paid {{pay_frequency}}
Signing Bonus: {{signing_bonus}} (if applicable)

3. BENEFITS
- Health Insurance: {{health_plan}}
- PTO Days: {{pto_days}} days per year
- 401(k) Match: {{retirement_match}}

4. CONFIDENTIALITY
Employee agrees to maintain confidentiality of all proprietary information during and after employment.

5. TERMINATION
Either party may terminate with {{notice_weeks}} weeks written notice.

GOVERNING LAW: {{governing_state}}
